            "text": "Brain Tumour Focus",
            "heading_size": "h3"
          }
        },
        "text_i8kkii": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><br/>At Alexandra Elizabeth, we believe jewellery should tell a story and create a lasting impact. We are proud to collaborate with renowned ballet dancer Jessica Matteo on a collection inspired by her extraordinary career, the relationships she has nurtured throughout her life, and the legacy she continues to share with her students and family. </p><p>Jessica and her husband, Dominic Matteo, are passionate supporters of Brain Tumour Focus, a charity dedicated to transforming brain tumour care and helping fund the UK's first portable MRI scanner for brain tumour patients. T</p><p>his pioneering technology has the potential to bring faster, more accessible and less distressing brain imaging directly to patients, improving both diagnosis and treatment outcomes. </p><p>As part of our commitment to this important cause, 10% of the profit from every piece sold within the Jessica Matteo Collection will be donated towards the Brain Tumour Focus portable MRI scanner fundraising campaign, helping to bring this life-changing innovation closer to reality. <br/><br/></p>"
          }
        }
