        "text_C3fyJk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Alexandra Elizabeth, we are incredibly proud to be a 1%er partner of the <a href=\"https://www.fortusfoundation.co.uk/become-a-1er?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" title=\"https://www.fortusfoundation.co.uk/\">Fortus Foundation,</a> an inspiring Yorkshire-based charity dedicated to supporting local communities, grassroots organisations, and small charities through meaningful funding and practical support. </p><p>As part of our commitment, we donate 1% of our profits through the Foundation's 1%er programme, ensuring that every piece of Alexandra Elizabeth jewellery contributes to positive change. </p><p>The Fortus Foundation helps businesses create a genuine social impact by directing funds to projects that improve education, support mental health, empower vulnerable groups, and strengthen local communities across Yorkshire.</p><p> By choosing Alexandra Elizabeth, our clients become part of this journey, helping us create beautiful jewellery while making a lasting difference where it is needed most<br/><br/></p>",
